metadata.name: The PACKAGE - Collector's Edition
metadata.description: "The PACKAGE - What could it be?" was self published on November 8th, 2022 by LBH Imaginarium, LLC. This children's book features Cool Cats #304 and #1039 along with Cool Pet #13650 from the Cool Cats NFT project. Also included are BAYC #3984 and BAKC #1486 from the Bored Ape Yacht Club and Bored Ape Kennel Club projects. This commemorative NFT was distributed to early supporters of "The PACKAGE".
